==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: nòng jiă chéng zhēn
===Idiom===
'''[[弄]][[假]][[成]][[真]]'''
# to turn simulation into reality unintentionally; fantasy becomes reality
#: ''[[校方]][[自備]][[人造]][[煙霧]][[熏倒]][[學生]][[消防]][[演習]]“'''弄假成真'''”''
#: ''[[校方]][[自备]][[人造]][[烟雾]][[熏倒]][[学生]][[消防]][[演习]]“'''弄假成真'''”''
#: '''''Fantasy becomes reality'''! School authorities create artifial smoke, cause students to faint from suffocation''

